---
// Download CTA section
---

<section class="section section-dark dl-section">
  <div class="container">
    <p class="dl-eyebrow">Get the app</p>
    <h2 class="dl-title">Ready to distill<br />your inbox?</h2>
    <p class="dl-sub">Download the latest APK. Install directly on any Android device.</p>
    <div class="dl-actions">
      <a href="https://github.com/shrivatsav-0/monomail/releases/latest" target="_blank" class="btn btn-primary">
        <svg width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
          <path d="M21 15v4a2 2 0 01-2 2H5a2 2 0 01-2-2v-4"/>
          <polyline points="7,10 12,15 17,10"/>
          <line x1="12" y1="15" x2="12" y2="3"/>
        </svg>
        Download Latest APK
      </a>
      <a href="https://github.com/shrivatsav-0/monomail" target="_blank" class="btn btn-ghost">
        <svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor">
          <path d="M12 2C6.477 2 2 6.484 2 12.017c0 4.425 2.865 8.18 6.839 9.504.5.092.682-.217.682-.483 0-.237-.008-.868-.013-1.703-2.782.605-3.369-1.343-3.369-1.343-.454-1.158-1.11-1.466-1.11-1.466-.908-.62.069-.608.069-.608 1.003.07 1.531 1.032 1.531 1.032.892 1.53 2.341 1.088 2.91.832.092-.647.35-1.088.636-1.338-2.22-.253-4.555-1.113-4.555-4.951 0-1.093.39-1.988 1.029-2.688-.103-.253-.446-1.272.098-2.65 0 0 .84-.27 2.75 1.026A9.564 9.564 0 0112 6.844c.85.004 1.705.115 2.504.337 1.909-1.296 2.747-1.027 2.747-1.027.546 1.379.202 2.398.1 2.651.64.7 1.028 1.595 1.028 2.688 0 3.848-2.339 4.695-4.566 4.943.359.309.678.92.678 1.855 0 1.338-.012 2.419-.012 2.747 0 .268.18.58.688.482A10.019 10.019 0 0022 12.017C22 6.484 17.522 2 12 2z"/>
        </svg>
        View Source
      </a>
    </div>
    <p class="dl-note">Android 8.0 (API 26) and above · Enable "Install unknown apps" in device settings</p>
    <div class="dl-flavor">
      <div class="dl-flavor-header">
        <svg width="15" height="15" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#666" stroke-width="1.8" stroke-linecap="round">
          <path d="M12 22s8-4 8-10V5l-8-3-8 3v7c0 6 8 10 8 10z"/><path d="M12 8v4"/><path d="M12 16h.01"/>
        </svg>
        Flavour differences
      </div>
      <p>Monomail comes in two versions. The Play Store version is in <strong class="dl-flavor-hl">closed testing</strong> right now. Join the test to get the full build.</p>

      <div class="dl-flavor-label">You'll miss on the GitHub build:</div>
      <div class="dl-flavor-loss">
        <div class="dl-flavor-loss-item">
          <svg width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#666" stroke-width="1.8" stroke-linecap="round"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"/><line x1="15" y1="9" x2="9" y2="15"/><line x1="9" y1="9" x2="15" y2="15"/></svg>
          <strong>Gmail account sign-in</strong> via Google OAuth
        </div>
        <div class="dl-flavor-loss-item">
          <svg width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#666" stroke-width="1.8" stroke-linecap="round"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"/><line x1="15" y1="9" x2="9" y2="15"/><line x1="9" y1="9" x2="15" y2="15"/></svg>
          <strong>Seamless setup</strong> with pre-configured OAuth credentials
        </div>
        <div class="dl-flavor-loss-item">
          <svg width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#666" stroke-width="1.8" stroke-linecap="round"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"/><line x1="15" y1="9" x2="9" y2="15"/><line x1="9" y1="9" x2="15" y2="15"/></svg>
          <strong>Push notifications</strong> (FCM requires Play Services)
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="dl-flavor-label">Still works:</div>
      <p><strong>Outlook</strong> and <strong>IMAP/SMTP</strong> accounts (Gmail, Yahoo, Zoho, etc.) work without restriction.</p>
      <p>To build the full flavour from source, see the <a href="https://github.com/shrivatsav-0/monomail" target="_blank">project README</a>.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
